  "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1104590/extras/example.jpg?t=1561060296\" ><br><u><strong>Bacillus</strong></u><br>Bacillus is an adventure game in which you go on the journey <br>to find a host! Along the way, you'll have to overcome countless<br>obstacles, eat the weak, <br>and avoid the strong ones.<br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1104590/extras/example2.jpg?t=1561060296\" ><br><strong><u>Merciless, sneaky and captivating</u></strong><br><br><br>ten different stages with different levels.<br>End stage is an open world stage in the human body<br>&quot;The dream of every bacillus&quot;.<br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1104590/extras/example3.jpg?t=1561060296\" ><br><strong><u>Varied and challenging</u></strong><br><br>various enemies such as simple bacillus, <br>mutated bacillus,<br> antiviruses, <br>defenses,<br> omnivorous parasites.<br><br><br><strong><u>if you have a host, it will take time to develop!</u></strong><br><br>Eat anything smaller than you to grow!<br>Eat certain mutant bacilli to mutate themselves and become stronger!",
